## ========= MODES ============
# Audio Troubleshooting
# When audio gets all messed up check out the command line mixer to config. alsamixer -c 0
# pacmd list sinks
# pactl list short sinks
## ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
